parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unavailability of parts for the Takata airbag recall can lead to delayed repairs, leaving drivers at risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: Airbag warning light illumination
inability to repair the vehicle due to parts unavailability.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Airbag sensor failure can cause the airbag to deploy unexpectedly, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: Airbag warning light illumination
unexpected airbag deployment.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission in reverse gear can cause the vehicle to become stuck, making it difficult or impossible to back up, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle will not shift into reverse gear
the reverse gear will not engage
the transmission will slip out of gear
the vehicle will not move when in reverse
the transmission warning light will illuminate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission in 5th gear can cause the vehicle to lose power, making it difficult to maintain speed, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission will slip out of 5th gear
the vehicle will lose power
the transmission warning light will illuminate
the vehicle will not shift into 5th gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Tire tread separation can cause loss of vehicle control, leading to accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: Tire tread separating from the tire
cracks around the tire
tire noise
vibration
and loss of control while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Sidewall splitting or herniation can cause tire failure, leading to loss of vehicle control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: Cracks or splits on the tire sidewall
tire bulging
and tire failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Excessive tire noise and vibration can be a sign of tire wear or damage, which can lead to tire failure and loss of vehicle control.
symptoms: Excessive tire noise
vibration while driving
and uneven tire wear.
